name: Step closer to the foe
description:
Sometimes the key to happiness is stepping closer to the foe and showing that you're bigger than it.

Mixed media art journal pages made in an upcycled modular planner, 9" x 7", 5481 x 4094 px, acrylic paint, vintage/found paper, ink. Cento composed with words found in Gregg Typing, New Series, 1953.
